  "title": "Global Warming: Challenges and Solutions",
  "html": "\n  <section class=\"slide\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 100vh; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <style>\n    .slide {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      justify-content: center;\n      align-items: center;\n      text-align: center;\n      background-color: var(--bg);\n      color: var(--text);\n      font-family: var(--font-body);\n      overflow: hidden;\n      position: relative;\n    }\n\n    .hero-content {\n      z-index: 2;\n      max-width: 80%;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n    }\n\n    .hero-title {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);\n      line-height: 1.1;\n      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n      color: var(--text);\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: -0.02em;\n    }\n\n    .hero-subtitle {\n      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n      line-height: 1.6;\n      max-width: 700px;\n      margin: 0 auto 2.5rem auto;\n    }\n\n    .cta-badge {\n      display: inline-block;\n      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;\n      border: 1px solid var(--accent);\n      color: var(--accent);\n      font-weight: 600;\n      border-radius: 4px;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 0.1em;\n      font-size: clamp(0.75rem, 1vw, 1rem);\n      box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--accent-glow);\n    }\n\n    .deco-ring {\n      position: absolute;\n      width: 60vh;\n      height: 60vh;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      opacity: 0.3;\n      z-index: 1;\n      animation: pulse 8s infinite ease-in-out;\n    }\n\n    .deco-ring::after {\n      content: '';\n      position: absolute;\n      top: -1px; left: -1px; right: -1px; bottom: -1px;\n      border: 1px solid var(--accent);\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      opacity: 0.5;\n      animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;\n    }\n\n    @keyframes pulse {\n      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.3; }\n      50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.1; }\n    }\n\n    @keyframes rotate {\n      from { transform: rotate(0deg); }\n      to { transform: rotate(360deg); }\n    }\n\n    .reveal {\n      opacity: 0;\n      transform: translateY(20px);\n      transition: all 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);\n    }\n\n    .reveal.active {\n      opacity: 1;\n      transform: translateY(0);\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <div class=\"deco-ring\"></div>\n\n  <div class=\"hero-content\">\n    <h1 class=\"hero-title reveal visible active\" style=\"--delay: 0.2s\">Global Warming: <br>Challenges and Solutions</h1>\n    <p class=\"hero-subtitle reveal visible active\" style=\"--delay: 0.4s\">\n      The climate crisis has reached a critical tipping point. As global temperatures continue to rise, our window to secure a sustainable future is narrowing.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"cta-badge reveal visible active\" style=\"--delay: 0.6s\">\n      Act Now for Tomorrow\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  \n</section>\n  \n\n\n  ",
